Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.30,0:16:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.40,0:16:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是能躲過我的攻擊的對手 不會不回敬我們就逃跑的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前方10點方向 魚雷音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.64,0:16:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,右舷全速 左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.83,0:16:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.63,0:16:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒中 打偏了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.61,0:16:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎全速掉頭中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.23,0:17:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次攻擊很快就來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.84,0:17:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.53,0:17:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長 瑪雅在那艘船上
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.90,0:17:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的魚雷 目的不是攻擊敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.48,0:17:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是為了"擊沉"巴魯丹諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.00,0:17:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的魚雷...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從魚雷的路線確認敵艦的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.05,0:17:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2號3號 裝填"沙魚"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.76,0:17:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.63,0:17:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認魚雷音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.72,0:17:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離魚雷命中目標 7秒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:58.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,6 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4 3
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2 1
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.70,0:18:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薩姆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爆炸音 命中巴魯丹諾斯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.95,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發送剛才的爆炸音到我的耳機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.18,0:18:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們肯定擊沉它了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.13,0:18:30.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成功了呢 艦長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.83,0:18:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.17,0:18:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.45,0:18:39.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴魯丹諾斯絲毫無損
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.51,0:18:41.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸彈爆炸之後並沒有船爆炸的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,船長？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.94,0:18:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們命中的 只是剛才我們特意射偏的魚雷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,趁此機會 我們進入他們的腹地
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.44,0:18:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那...那到底是...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.89,0:18:53.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,速度 在他們發射脈衝之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發射主動聲納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.50,0:18:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經發射了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:18:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.70,0:19:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.75,0:19:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們就在我們肚子底下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.46,0:19:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.75,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"擊沉"巴魯丹諾斯 就是這個意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦深度 200
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.34,0:19:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深沙炸彈6 深度190 195 200
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.97,0:19:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投放
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,投放深沙炸彈的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.56,0:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.65,0:19:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,方位 0 正上方200
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.87,0:19:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.92,0:19:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向上90度
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.34,0:19:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9...90？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.97,0:19:32.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟他們撞個滿懷！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦 小的們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.99,0:19:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確認敵艦鍋爐音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.99,0:19:39.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前進路線是？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.23,0:19:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鍋爐音增大 在上浮中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.84,0:19:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引擎全速 倆舷掉頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:46.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為何後退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.26,0:19:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們想撞翻這艘艦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.25,0:19:53.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.51,0:19:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,倆舷全速
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.38,0:19:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.72,0:20:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我撞！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.20,0:20:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.05,0:20:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,噪音太多 不能辨別
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.07,0:20:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.64,0:20:40.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是敵艦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.22,0:21:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是巴魯丹諾斯的船長嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生啥事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.89,0:23:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,主顯示器被破壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.65,0:23:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,傳感器沒有壞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.37,0:23:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,周圍有空間
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.81,0:23:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎巴魯丹諾斯闖進了OZMA的肚子裏
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是"心臟"嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.95,0:23:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們將面臨怎樣的命運？
